🚀 AI Personal Portfolio Website

A modern and responsive personal portfolio website built using HTML, Tailwind CSS, and JavaScript. This portfolio showcases my skills, projects, achievements, and contact information with an elegant UI and Dark/Light mode support.

✨ Features

- Modern and premium design
- Fully responsive layout
- Dark and Light mode toggle
- Typing animation in Hero section
- Animated skill bars
- Projects showcase cards
- Achievements and Certifications section
- Contact section with direct links
- Smooth scrolling animations
- Active navigation highlighting
- SEO optimized
- Single HTML file
- Tailwind CSS CDN integration

🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5
- Tailwind CSS
- JavaScript
- Font Awesome
- Google Fonts

